<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-32-1096 </DOCNO><TEXT>The use of fossil fuels and their environmental effects are considered.The increase of carbon dioxide in the atmosphere confirms future damageon climatic conditions. This paper considers how the use of alternativeenergy sources and the use of nuclear energy can reduce these effects.The author cites the development of intrinsically safe reactors as themost realistic and effective solution.</TEXT></DOC>